OL,7,FWelsh Ministers have been concerned
OL,8,Fabout the method the UK Treasury is
OL,9,Fusing to calculate that amount.
OL,11,FIt relies on the Barnett Formula - a
OL,12,Fmethod used to work out how much
OL,13,Ffunding Wales should get based on
OL,14,Fspending in England.
OL,16,FBut because the public sector is
OL,17,Fbigger here in Wales than across the
OL,18,Fborder, Welsh ministers argued that
OL,19,Fusing the formula in this instance
OL,20,Fwould leave Wales shortchanged.
